query:
INSERT INTO transfer (
                    initiator_id, 
                    from_account_id, 
                    to_account_id, 
                    transaction_id, 
                    amount, 
                    note
                ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?) 
                RETURNING 
                    id, 
                    initiator_id, 
                    from_account_id, 
                    to_account_id, 
                    transaction_id, 
                    ? as "transaction_timestamp!: _", 
                    amount as "amount: _", 
                    note
